# Image Placeholders

This directory contains project images. Replace these placeholders with your actual project photos.

## Recommended Image Specs

- **Dimensions**: 800x600px (4:3 ratio)
- **Format**: JPG or PNG
- **File Size**: < 500KB (compress with TinyPNG)
- **Naming**: Use lowercase with hyphens (e.g., `smart-home-hub.jpg`)

