## Placeholder Image

If you don't have an image yet, create a simple placeholder:
- **Tool**: [placeholder.com](https://placeholder.com)
- **Example**: `https://via.placeholder.com/800x600/1a1f3a/00ff9f?text=Project+Name`

Or use a screenshot of your project, circuit diagram, or related image.
